02:41.440 --> 02:49.210
blanket with a soldier on either side of them 
sleeping on their guns. And when the men came up the

02:49.911 --> 02:56.139
trail at 10 o'clock at night, one of them said, Kim 
Beebe, who comes? And one of them said, Carranza.

03:00.425 --> 03:01.867
And the other said, Villa. So they were evidently 
divided, you see. The men who were holding him

03:05.292 --> 03:10.198
claimed to be The men who were holding him came to be 
viestas and they arranged then for the ransom to be

03:10.364 --> 03:23.107
paid out of the, from the mining company office in 
