12:46.679 --> 12:53.369
a patio effect out in front, and when it was warm 
weather, they would live out in this patio. And

12:53.389 --> 12:56.153
when it was cold, they'd go back in the hillside. 
Very friendly. And these were the people that

12:57.395 --> 13:01.081
worked in the mines? Yes, yes, those were the 
