32:13.265 --> 32:18.151
It's just a series of that sort of thing. And of 
course, during the time that he was down there, it

32:18.212 --> 32:23.899
was all so... revolutionary, you know.

32:30.736 --> 32:33.081
Not nearly as stable as it is now. Of course, they 
say it isn't too good, but it's a lot more stable

32:33.101 --> 32:38.551
than it was then. At least they have a set 
government now that seems to work.

