33:25.456 --> 33:37.391
clerk that was waiting down there came with 
Medellin, and I said, did you happen to come from

33:25.456 --> 33:37.391
the Medellin family in the garrison? He said, yes, 
that was my father. Wasn't that queer? How did he

33:42.757 --> 33:44.059
happen to come? Well, I think the whole family came 
up here, and they were living out on the... I knew of

33:50.287 --> 33:52.670
them, and I knew when they came. I mean, I... Mr. 
Adams had known of their being here, and that the

33:54.025 --> 33:59.271
whole family came up here. He was a good mechanic. 
Of course, I don't know of what sort of, you say he

34:01.554 --> 34:12.967
would have in, in, in locating here, but he 
