35:18.130 --> 35:29.228
He went to Houston first with the law firm there, 
and then he went on to Washington as the Assistant

35:18.130 --> 35:29.228
Secretary for Latin America. What is his name? 
Collin. Henry Collin.

35:38.604 --> 35:41.168
They had a very interesting experience. three 
years at the embassy

35:41.587 --> 35:46.031
in Mexico City. In fact, Henry spoke such good 
Spanish, that was when Mr. Messerschmitt was the

35:46.051 --> 35:55.241
ambassador

35:46.051 --> 35:55.241
in Mexico. Henry spoke such good Spanish that he 
